name: Resource Reasoning
body:
This is a holding page for the [Resource Reasoning GitHub organisation](https://github.com/resource-reasoning/) repositories.
You may find more information about Resource Reasoning at either resourcereasoning.com for the UK-wide Resource Reasoning research community, or the [Imperial College Group's homepage](http://www-lrr.doc.ic.ac.uk/).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
